# .trivyignore — suppressed Trivy findings
#
# Each entry must include:
#   1. A comment explaining why it is suppressed
#   2. An expiry date so suppressions don't become permanent
#
# Format:
#   # <reason>
#   # expires: YYYY-MM-DD
#   CVE-XXXX-XXXXX
#
# Example (remove when adding a real entry):
#   # CVE-2024-12345: no fix available in Ubuntu 24.04 as of today
#   # expires: 2026-07-01
#   CVE-2024-12345
